title: "CaseForge (public-llmCaseGen-CIKM2026)"
abstract: >
  Faculty-facing browser tool that drafts personalised professional case
  studies via a four-stage RAG+LLM pipeline (Input, Retrieval, Generation,
  Faculty-in-the-loop editing) with discipline packs for Finance, Marketing,
  and Social Work.
